thread.title_full: Public Storage reviewed by Julia Bailey

author: Julia Bailey
title: Julia Bailey
text: Janice was amazing! She anticipated our needs, showing us two units (one we reserved and one a bit larger). She was spot on and we went with the larger unit! She was friendly and made the process easy and enjoyable. Would recommend her service and the units in a heartbeat!
